Do you have to be ghosts?

9
00:01:09,560 --> 00:01:10,510
What? Don't touch me!

10
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:13,310
Are you kidding me?
How can you blame me?

11
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:15,030
You asked them

12
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:17,350
to pose as ghosts for the apartments!

13
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:18,670
Listen,

14
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:21,070
