Hurry up. Come on.

22
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:42,950
Little kid, it's over. Stop acting.

23
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,150
He's my son.

24
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:48,310
Your son?
That's great. I don't need to pay him.

25
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:49,600
Over here.

26
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,030
Good job.

27
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,470
Ghost!

28
00:02:03,950 --> 00:02:04,790
Ghost!

29
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,520
Come on.

30
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:14,200
He's moving so slowly.
Did you pay him too little?

31
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:17,790
Are you kidding me?

32
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:20,670
This big show cost me a lot of money.

33
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:23,150
