34
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,310
How could he afford to hire anyone?

35
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:27,350
He even paid me buns instead of money.

36
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,670
Then who is he?

37
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,030
Xiaodao?

38
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:11,910
What are you doing?

39
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:13,590
It's none of your business!

40
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:15,070
You're making it worse!

41
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:16,950
You got nothing to do?

42
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:20,510
If I can't get the apartment,
will you support me?

43
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,590
Do you know how hard I've tried
to make money

44
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:23,950
to go back to my hometown?

45
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:26,230
Can't you just be
an obedient security guard?

46
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:28,030
Do you understand?

47
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:30,670
- Answer me!
- Say something!

48
00:03:33,590 --> 00:03:34,430
Xiaodao!

49
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,230
Xiaodao!

50
00:03:41,540 --> 00:03:42,380
Xiaodao!

51
00:03:43,230 --> 00:03:44,800
I didn't do it! It wasn't me!

52
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:45,670
You're doomed.

53
00:03:46,770 --> 00:03:47,620
This...

54
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:53,910
Xiaodao!

55
00:03:54,210 --> 00:03:55,050
Xiaodao!

56
00:03:55,390 --> 00:03:56,340
Xiaodao!

57
00:03:57,450 --> 00:03:58,330
Xiaodao!

58
00:03:58,590 --> 00:03:59,710
Brother Xiaodao!

59
00:04:03,940 --> 00:04:05,560
Brother Xiaodao!

60
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:07,320
Brother Xiaodao!

61
00:04:07,990 --> 00:04:09,470
Brother Xiaodao!

62
00:04:09,650 --> 00:04:11,640
Brother Xiaodao!

63
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:15,970
- Brother Xiaodao!
- Xiaodao!

64
00:04:16,220 --> 00:04:18,030
Tang Yuanbao, you're over.

65
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,310
He's dead.

66
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:21,190
How are you going to pay compensation?

67
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,310
What compensation?

68
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,470
I didn't...

69
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,520
I didn't push him.

70
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:25,510
We all saw you

71
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:28,270
