72
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,390
It was you!

73
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:30,910
Didn't you push him?

74
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,750
I saw it! You pushed him hard!

75
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:37,830
I only touched him lightly.

76
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:39,510
Anyway,

77
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:40,430
he's dead now.

78
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,030
Give us money and apartments,

79
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,430
or we won't go easy on you!

80
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:44,280
Nonsense!

81
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:46,230
Shut up, both of you!

82
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:49,830
Why are you so heartless?

83
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:54,510
Mr... Mr. Tang.

84
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:56,280
Why are you here?

85
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:59,790
- Ghost!
- There's a ghost!

86
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,470
Enough, Frank.

87
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:03,750
You've done your job, okay?

88
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:08,470
It's real!
Her head can shrink into her body!

89
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,710
What's that?

90
00:05:17,530 --> 00:05:18,890
Ghost!

91
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,030
